<h2>
    Hackable, download-free  demos of the PIA web language
</h2>
<p>
    Active XML tags (like
    <code>&lt;if></code>
    or
    <code>&lt;include></code>
    ) allow web pages to perform their own processing
    and recursive reference, without the need for separate CGI scripting
    programs or languages.
</p>
<p>
    <b>
        The best way to understand this new approach is to play with
    it
    </b>
    , by trying a demo and watching how your modifications appear as
    processed output.
</p>
